\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\ql\rtlch\af10\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af7\langfe255\hich\fs24\lang1066\loch\fs24\lang1066 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs28\lang1066\i0\b0 Tr\u259\'3fm n\u259\'3fm trong c\'f5i ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi ta,\line Ch\u7919\'3f t\'e0i ch\u7919\'3f m\u7879\'3fnh kh\'e9o l\'e0 gh\'e9t nhau.\line Tr\u7843\'3fi qua m\u7897\'3ft cu\u7897\'3fc b\u7875\'3f d\'e2u,\line Nh\u7919\'3fng \u273\'3fi\u7873\'3fu tr\'f4ng th\u7845\'3fy m\'e0 \u273\'3fau \u273\'3f\u7899\'3fn l\'f2ng.\line 5L\u7841\'3f g\'ec b\u7881\'3f s\u7855\'3fc t\u432\'3f phong,\line Tr\u7901\'3fi xanh quen th\'f3i m\'e1 h\u7891\'3fng \u273\'3f\'e1nh ghen.\line C\u7843\'3fo th\u417\'3fm l\u7847\'3fn gi\u7903\'3f tr\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc \u273\'3f\'e8n,\line Phong t\'ecnh c\'f3 l\u7909\'3fc c\'f2n truy\u7873\'3fn s\u7917\'3f xan
h.\line R\u7857\'3fng n\u259\'3fm Gia T\u297\'3fnh tri\u7873\'3fu Minh,\line 10B\u7889\'3fn ph\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng ph\u7859\'3fng l\u7863\'3fng, hai kinh v\u7919\'3fng v\'e0ng.\line C\'f3 nh\'e0 vi\'ean ngo\u7841\'3fi h\u7885\'3f V\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng,\line Gia t\u432\'3f ngh\u7881\'3f c\u361\'3fng th\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fng th\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fng b\u7921\'3fc trung.\line M\u7897\'3ft trai con th\u7913\'3f r\u7889\'3ft l\'f2ng,\line V\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng Quan l\'e0 ch\u7919\'3f, n\u7889\'3fi d\'f2ng nho gia.\line 15\u272\'3f\u7847\'3fu l\'f2ng hai \u7843\'3f t\u7889\'3f nga,\line Th\'fay Ki\u7873\'3fu l\'e0 ch\u7883\'3f, e
m l\'e0 Th\'fay V\'e2n.\line Mai c\u7889\'3ft c\'e1ch, tuy\u7871\'3ft tinh th\u7847\'3fn,\line M\u7895\'3fi ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi m\u7897\'3ft v\u7867\'3f, m\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi ph\'e2n v\u7865\'3fn m\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi.\line V\'e2n xem trang tr\u7885\'3fng kh\'e1c v\u7901\'3fi,\line 20Khu\'f4n tr\u259\'3fng \u273\'3f\u7847\'3fy \u273\'3f\u7863\'3fn, n\'e9t ng\'e0i n\u7903\'3f nang.\line Hoa c\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi ng\u7885\'3fc th\u7889\'3ft \u273\'3foan trang,\line M\'e2y thua n\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc t\'f3c, tuy\u7871\'3ft nh\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fng m\'e0u da.\line Ki\u7873\'3fu c\'e0ng s\u7855\'3fc s\u7843\'3fo, m\u7863\'3fn m\'e0,\line So 
b\u7873\'3f t\'e0i, s\u7855\'3fc, l\u7841\'3fi l\'e0 ph\u7847\'3fn h\u417\'3fn.\line 25L\'e0n thu th\u7911\'3fy, n\'e9t xu\'e2n s\u417\'3fn,\line Hoa ghen thua th\u7855\'3fm, li\u7877\'3fu h\u7901\'3fn k\'e9m xanh.\line M\u7897\'3ft, hai nghi\'eang n\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc nghi\'eang th\'e0nh,\line S\u7855\'3fc \u273\'3f\'e0nh \u273\'3f\'f2i m\u7897\'3ft, t\'e0i \u273\'3f\'e0nh h\u7885\'3fa hai.\line Th\'f4ng minh v\u7889\'3fn s\u7861\'3fn t\u432\'3f tr\u7901\'3fi,\line 30Pha ngh\u7873\'3f thi h\u7885\'3fa, \u273\'3f\u7911\'3f m\'f9i ca ng\'e2m.\line Cung th\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng l\'e0u b\u7853\'3fc 
ng\u361\'3f \'e2m,\line Ngh\u7873\'3f ri\'eang \u259\'3fn \u273\'3f\u7913\'3ft H\u7891\'3f c\u7847\'3fm m\u7897\'3ft tr\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng.\line Kh\'fac nh\'e0 tay l\u7921\'3fa n\'ean ch\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng,\line M\u7897\'3ft thi\'ean b\u7841\'3fc m\u7879\'3fnh, l\u7841\'3fi c\'e0ng n\'e3o nh\'e2n.\line 35Phong l\u432\'3fu r\u7845\'3ft m\u7921\'3fc h\u7891\'3fng qu\u7847\'3fn,\line Xu\'e2n xanh s\u7845\'3fp x\u7881\'3f t\u7899\'3fi tu\u7847\'3fn c\u7853\'3fp k\'ea\line \'cam \u273\'3f\u7873\'3fm tr\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fng r\u7911\'3f m\'e0n che,\line T\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fng \u273\'3f\'f4ng ong b\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fm \u273\'3fi v\u7873\'3f m\u7863\'3fc ai.\line Ng\'e0y xu\'e2n con \'e9n \u273\'3f\u432\'3f
a thoi,\line 40Thi\u7873\'3fu quang ch\'edn ch\u7909\'3fc \u273\'3f\'e3 ngo\'e0i s\'e1u m\u432\'3f\u417\'3fi.\line C\u7887\'3f non xanh t\u7853\'3fn ch\'e2n tr\u7901\'3fi,\line C\'e0nh l\'ea tr\u7855\'3fng \u273\'3fi\u7875\'3fm m\u7897\'3ft v\'e0i b\'f4ng hoa.\line Thanh minh trong ti\u7871\'3ft th\'e1ng ba,\line L\u7877\'3f l\'e0 t\u7843\'3fo m\u7897\'3f, h\u7897\'3fi l\'e0 \u273\'3f\u7841\'3fp Thanh.\line 45G\u7847\'3fn xa n\'f4 n\u7913\'3fc y\u7871\'3fn anh,\line Ch\u7883\'3f em s\u7855\'3fm s\u7917\'3fa b\u7897\'3f h\'e0nh ch\u417\'3fi xu\'e2n.\line D\u7853\'3fp d\'ecu t\'e0i t\u7917\'3f, gi
ai nh\'e2n,\line Ng\u7921\'3fa xe nh\u432\'3f n\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc \'e1o qu\u7847\'3fn nh\u432\'3f n\'eam.\line Ng\u7893\'3fn ngang g\'f2 \u273\'3f\u7889\'3fng k\'e9o l\'ean,\line 50Thoi v\'e0ng v\'f3 r\u7855\'3fc tro ti\u7873\'3fn gi\u7845\'3fy bay.\line T\'e0 t\'e0 b\'f3ng ng\u7843\'3f v\u7873\'3f t\'e2y,\line Ch\u7883\'3f em th\u417\'3f th\u7849\'3fn dan tay ra v\u7873\'3f.\line B\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc d\u7847\'3fn theo ng\u7885\'3fn ti\u7875\'3fu kh\'ea,\line L\u7847\'3fn xem phong c\u7843\'3fnh c\'f3 b\u7873\'3f thanh thanh.\line 55Nao nao d\'f2ng n\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc u\u7889\'3fn qu
anh,\line D\u7883\'3fp c\u7847\'3fu nho nh\u7887\'3f cu\u7889\'3fi gh\u7873\'3fnh b\u7855\'3fc ngang.\line S\'e8 s\'e8 n\u7845\'3fm \u273\'3f\u7845\'3ft b\'ean \u273\'3f\'e0ng,\line D\'e0u d\'e0u ng\u7885\'3fn c\u7887\'3f n\u7917\'3fa v\'e0ng n\u7917\'3fa xanh.\line R\u7857\'3fng: Sao trong ti\u7871\'3ft thanh minh,\line 60M\'e0 \u273\'3f\'e2y h\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng kh\'f3i v\u7855\'3fng tanh th\u7871\'3f m\'e0?\line V\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng Quan m\u7899\'3fi d\u7851\'3fn g\u7847\'3fn xa:\line \u272\'3f\u7841\'3fm Ti\'ean n\'e0ng \u7845\'3fy x\u432\'3fa l\'e0 ca nhi.\line N\u7893\'3fi danh t\'e0i s\u7855\'3fc m\u7897\'3ft th\'ec
,\line X\'f4n xao ngo\'e0i c\u7917\'3fa hi\u7871\'3fm g\'ec y\u7871\'3fn anh.\line 65Ki\u7871\'3fp h\u7891\'3fng nhan c\'f3 mong manh,\line N\u7917\'3fa ch\u7915\'3fng xu\'e2n tho\u7855\'3ft g\'e3y c\'e0nh thi\'ean h\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng.\line C\'f3 ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi kh\'e1ch \u7903\'3f vi\u7877\'3fn ph\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng,\line Xa nghe c\u361\'3fng n\u7913\'3fc ti\u7871\'3fng n\'e0ng t\'ecm ch\u417\'3fi.\line Thuy\u7873\'3fn t\'ecnh v\u7915\'3fa gh\'e9 t\u7899\'3fi n\u417\'3fi,\line 70Th\'ec \u273\'3f\'e0 tr\'e2m g\u7851\'3fy b\'ecnh r\u417\'3fi bao gi\u7901\'3f.\line Bu\u7891\'3fng kh\'f4ng 
l\u7841\'3fnh ng\u7855\'3ft nh\u432\'3f t\u7901\'3f,\line D\u7845\'3fu xe ng\u7921\'3fa \u273\'3f\'e3 r\'eau l\u7901\'3f m\u7901\'3f xanh.\line Kh\'f3c than kh\'f4n xi\u7871\'3ft s\u7921\'3f t\'ecnh,\line Kh\'e9o v\'f4 duy\'ean \u7845\'3fy l\'e0 m\'ecnh v\u7899\'3fi ta.\line 75\u272\'3f\'e3 kh\'f4ng duy\'ean tr\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc ch\u259\'3fng m\'e0,\line Th\'ec chi ch\'fat \u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc g\u7885\'3fi l\'e0 duy\'ean sau.\line S\u7855\'3fm xanh n\u7871\'3fp t\u7917\'3f xe ch\'e2u,\line V\'f9i n\'f4ng m\u7897\'3ft n\u7845\'3fm m\u7863\'3fc d\u7847\'3fu c\u7887\'3f hoa.\line Tr\u7843\'3fi bao th\u7887\'3f l\u7863\'3fn \'e1c
 t\'e0,\line 80\u7845\'3fy m\u7891\'3f v\'f4 ch\u7911\'3f, ai m\'e0 vi\u7871\'3fng th\u259\'3fm!\line L\'f2ng \u273\'3f\'e2u s\u7861\'3fn m\u7889\'3fi th\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng t\'e2m,\line Tho\u7855\'3ft nghe Ki\u7873\'3fu \u273\'3f\'e3 \u273\'3f\u7847\'3fm \u273\'3f\u7847\'3fm ch\'e2u sa.\line \u272\'3fau \u273\'3f\u7899\'3fn thay ph\u7853\'3fn \u273\'3f\'e0n b\'e0!\line L\u7901\'3fi r\u7857\'3fng b\u7841\'3fc m\u7879\'3fnh c\u361\'3fng l\'e0 l\u7901\'3fi chung.\line 85Ph\u361\'3f ph\'e0ng chi b\u7845\'3fy h\'f3a c\'f4ng,\line Ng\'e0y xanh m\'f2n m\u7887\'3fi m\'e1 h\u7891\'3fng ph\'f4i pha.\line S\u7889\'3fng l\'e0m v\u7907\'3f kh\u7855\'3fp ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi 
ta,\line Kh\'e9o thay th\'e1c xu\u7889\'3fng l\'e0m ma kh\'f4ng ch\u7891\'3fng.\line N\'e0o ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi ph\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fng ch\u7841\'3f loan chung,\line 90N\'e0o ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi t\'edch l\u7909\'3fc tham h\u7891\'3fng l\'e0 ai\~?\line \u272\'3f\'e3 kh\'f4ng k\u7867\'3f \u273\'3fo\'e1i ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi ho\'e0i,\line S\u7861\'3fn \u273\'3f\'e2y ta ki\u7871\'3fm m\u7897\'3ft v\'e0i n\'e9n h\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng.\line G\u7885\'3fi l\'e0 g\u7863\'3fp g\u7905\'3f gi\u7919\'3fa \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fng,\line H\u7885\'3fa l\'e0 ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi d\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fi su\u7889\'3fi v\'e0ng bi\u7871\'3ft cho.\line 95L\u7847\'3fm r\u7847\'3fm k
h\u7845\'3fn kh\u7913\'3fa nh\u7887\'3f to,\line S\u7909\'3fp ng\u7891\'3fi v\'e0i g\u7853\'3ft tr\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc m\u7891\'3f b\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc ra.\line M\u7897\'3ft v\'f9ng c\u7887\'3f \'e1y b\'f3ng t\'e0,\line Gi\'f3 hiu hiu th\u7893\'3fi m\u7897\'3ft v\'e0i b\'f4ng lau.\line R\'fat tr\'e2m s\u7861\'3fn gi\u7855\'3ft m\'e1i \u273\'3f\u7847\'3fu,\line 100V\u7841\'3fch da c\'e2y v\u7883\'3fnh b\u7889\'3fn c\'e2u ba v\u7847\'3fn.\line L\u7841\'3fi c\'e0ng m\'ea m\u7849\'3fn t\'e2m th\u7847\'3fn\line L\u7841\'3fi c\'e0ng \u273\'3f\u7913\'3fng l\u7863\'3fng t\u7847\'3fn ng\u7847\'3fn ch\u7859\'3fng ra.\line L\u7841\'3fi c\'e0ng \u7911\'3f d\u7897\'3ft n\'e9t 
