\u7857\'3fng mai c\'f3 nh\u432\'3f r\'e0y cho ch\u259\'3fng!\line 1025S\u7907\'3f khi ong b\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fm \u273\'3f\'e3i \u273\'3f\u7857\'3fng,\line \u272\'3f\u7871\'3fn \u273\'3fi\u7873\'3fu s\u7889\'3fng \u273\'3f\u7909\'3fc, sao b\u7857\'3fng th\'e1c trong!\line M\u7909\'3f r\u7857\'3fng: Con h\'e3y thong dong,\line Ph\u7843\'3fi \u273\'3fi\u7873\'3fu l\'f2ng l\u7841\'3fi d\u7889\'3fi l\'f2ng m\'e0 ch\u417\'3fi!\line Mai sau \u7903\'3f ch\u7859\'3fng nh\u432\'3f l\u7901\'3fi,\line 1030Tr\'ean \u273\'3f\u7847\'3fu c\'f3 b\'f3ng m\u7863\'3ft tr\u7901\'3fi r\u7841\'3fng soi.\line Th\u7845\'3fy l\u7901\'3fi quy\u7871\'3ft \u273\'3fo\'e1n h\u7859\'3fn h
oi,\line \u272\'3f\'e0nh l\'f2ng, n\'e0ng c\u361\'3fng s\u7869\'3f ngu\'f4i ngu\'f4i d\u7847\'3fn.\line Tr\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc l\u7847\'3fu Ng\u432\'3fng b\'edch kh\'f3a xu\'e2n,\line V\u7867\'3f non xa, t\u7845\'3fm tr\u259\'3fng g\u7847\'3fn, \u7903\'3f chung.\line 1035B\u7889\'3fn b\u7873\'3f b\'e1t ng\'e1t xa tr\'f4ng,\line C\'e1t v\'e0ng c\u7891\'3fn n\u7885\'3f, b\u7909\'3fi h\u7891\'3fng d\u7863\'3fm kia.\line B\u7869\'3f b\'e0ng m\'e2y s\u7899\'3fm \u273\'3f\'e8n khuya,\line N\u7917\'3fa t\'ecnh, n\u7917\'3fa c\u7843\'3fnh nh\u432\'3f chia t\u7845\'3fm l\'f2ng.\line T\u432\'3f\u7903\'3fng ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi d\u432\'3f
