\u7899\'3fi bi\u7871\'3ft r\u7857\'3fng ch\'e0ng S\u7903\'3f Khanh.\line B\'f3ng Nga th\u7845\'3fp tho\'e1ng d\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fi m\'e0nh,\line Tr\'f4ng n\'e0ng, ch\'e0ng c\u361\'3fng ra t\'ecnh \u273\'3feo \u273\'3fai.\line 1065Than \'f4i! S\u7855\'3fc n\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc h\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng tr\u7901\'3fi,\line Ti\u7871\'3fc cho \u273\'3f\'e2u b\u7895\'3fng l\u7841\'3fc lo\'e0i \u273\'3f\u7871\'3fn \u273\'3f\'e2y\~?\line Gi\'e1 \u273\'3f\'e0nh trong nguy\u7879\'3ft tr\'ean m\'e2y,\line Hoa sao, hoa kh\'e9o \u273\'3f\u7885\'3fa \u273\'3f\'e0y b\u7845\'3fy hoa\~?\line T\u7913\'3fc gan ri\'eang gi
\u7853\'3fn tr\u7901\'3fi gi\'e0,\line 1070L\'f2ng n\'e0y ai t\u7887\'3f cho ta, h\u7905\'3fi l\'f2ng?\line Thuy\u7873\'3fn quy\'ean v\'ed bi\u7871\'3ft anh h\'f9ng,\line Ra tay th\'e1o c\u361\'3fi, s\u7893\'3f l\u7891\'3fng nh\u432\'3f ch\u417\'3fi!\line Song thu \u273\'3f\'e3 kh\'e9p c\'e1nh ngo\'e0i,\line Tai c\'f2n \u273\'3f\u7891\'3fng v\u7885\'3fng m\u7845\'3fy l\u7901\'3fi s\u7855\'3ft \u273\'3fanh.\line 1075Ngh\u297\'3f ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi th\'f4i l\u7841\'3fi ngh\u297\'3f m\'ecnh,\line C\'e1m l\'f2ng chua x\'f3t, nh\u7841\'3ft t\'ecnh ch\u417\'3f v\u417\'3f.\line Nh\u7919\'3f
ng l\'e0 l\u7847\'3fn l\u7919\'3fa n\u7855\'3fng m\u432\'3fa,\line Ki\u7871\'3fp phong tr\u7847\'3fn bi\u7871\'3ft bao gi\u7901\'3f m\u7899\'3fi th\'f4i\~?\line \u272\'3f\'e1nh li\u7873\'3fu nh\u7855\'3fn m\u7897\'3ft hai l\u7901\'3fi,\line 1080Nh\u7901\'3f tay t\u7871\'3f \u273\'3f\u7897\'3f v\u7899\'3ft ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi tr\u7847\'3fm lu\'e2n.\line M\u7843\'3fnh ti\'ean k\u7875\'3f h\u7871\'3ft xa g\u7847\'3fn,\line N\u7895\'3fi nh\'e0 b\'e1o \u273\'3f\'e1p, n\u7895\'3fi th\'e2n l\u7841\'3fc lo\'e0i.\line Tan s\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng v\u7915\'3fa r\u7841\'3fng ng\'e0y mai,\line Ti\u7879\'3fn h\u7891\'3fng n\'e0ng m\u7899\'3fi nh\u7855\'3fn l\u7901\'3fi g\u7917\'3fi san
