nh v\u7873\'3f sau!\line L\u7863\'3fng nghe, l\u7849\'3fm nh\u7849\'3fm g\u7853\'3ft \u273\'3f\u7847\'3fu:\line Ta \u273\'3f\'e2y ph\u7843\'3fi m\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fn ai \u273\'3f\'e2u m\'e0 r\u7857\'3fng!\line N\'e0ng \u273\'3f\'e0 bi\u7871\'3ft \u273\'3f\u7871\'3fn ta ch\u259\'3fng,\line B\u7875\'3f tr\u7847\'3fm lu\'e2n, l\u7845\'3fp cho b\u7857\'3fng m\u7899\'3fi th\'f4i!\line 1105N\'e0ng r\u7857\'3fng: Mu\'f4n s\u7921\'3f \u417\'3fn ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi,\line Th\u7871\'3f n\'e0o xin quy\u7871\'3ft m\u7897\'3ft b\'e0i cho xong.\line R\u7857\'3fng: Ta c\'f3 ng\u7921\'3fa truy phong,\line C\'f3 t\'ean d\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fi tr\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fng, v
