 \u273\'3f\'e2u \u273\'3f\'e3 m\'e1i sau d\u7853\'3fy d\'e0ng.\line 1125N\'e0ng c\'e0ng th\u7893\'3fn th\u7913\'3fc gan v\'e0ng,\line S\u7903\'3f Khanh \u273\'3f\'e3 r\u7869\'3f d\'e2y c\u432\'3f\u417\'3fng l\u7889\'3fi n\'e0o!\line M\u7897\'3ft m\'ecnh kh\'f4n bi\u7871\'3ft l\'e0m sao,\line D\u7863\'3fm r\u7915\'3fng b\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc th\u7845\'3fp, b\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc cao h\'e3i h\'f9ng.\line H\'f3a nhi th\u7853\'3ft c\'f3 n\u7905\'3f l\'f2ng,\line 1130L\'e0m chi d\'e0y t\'eda, v\'f2 h\u7891\'3fng, l\u7855\'3fm nau!\line M\u7897\'3ft \u273\'3fo\'e0n \u273\'3f\u7893\'3f \u273\'3f\u7871\'3fn tr\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc sau,\line Vu\u7889\'3ft
