u,\line 1140U\u7889\'3fn l\u432\'3fng th\u7883\'3ft \u273\'3f\u7893\'3f, c\u7845\'3ft \u273\'3f\u7847\'3fu m\'e1u sa.\line R\u7857\'3fng: T\'f4i ch\'fat ph\u7853\'3fn \u273\'3f\'e0n b\'e0,\line N\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc non l\'eca c\u7917\'3fa, l\'eca nh\'e0, \u273\'3f\u7871\'3fn \u273\'3f\'e2y.\line B\'e2y gi\u7901\'3f s\u7889\'3fng ch\u7871\'3ft \u7903\'3f tay,\line Th\'e2n n\'e0y \u273\'3f\'e3 \u273\'3f\u7871\'3fn th\u7871\'3f n\'e0y th\'ec th\'f4i!\line 1145Nh\u432\'3fng t\'f4i c\'f3 s\'e1 chi t\'f4i,\line Ph\u7853\'3fn t\'f4i \u273\'3f\'e0nh v\u7853\'3fy, v\u7889\'3fn ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi \u273\'3f\u7875\'3f \u273\'3f\'e2u\~?\line Th\'e2n l\u432\'3f\u417\'3fn bao qu\u7843\'3fn l\u7845\'3fm \u273\'3f\u7847\'3f
u,\line Ch\'fat l\'f2ng trinh b\u7841\'3fch t\u7915\'3f sau xin ch\u7915\'3fa!\line \u272\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc l\u7901\'3fi m\u7909\'3f m\u7899\'3fi t\'f9y c\u417\'3f,\line 1150B\u7855\'3ft ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi b\u7843\'3fo l\u297\'3fnh l\'e0m t\u7901\'3f cung chi\'eau.\line B\'e0y vai c\'f3 \u7843\'3f M\'e3 Ki\u7873\'3fu,\line X\'f3t n\'e0ng, ra m\u7899\'3fi \u273\'3f\'e1nh li\u7873\'3fu ch\u7883\'3fu \u273\'3foan.\line M\u7909\'3f c\'e0ng k\u7875\'3f nh\u7863\'3ft, k\u7875\'3f khoan,\line G\u7841\'3fn g\'f9ng \u273\'3f\u7871\'3fn m\u7921\'3fc, n\u7891\'3fng n\'e0n m\u7899\'3fi tha.\line 1155V\u7921\'3fc n\'e0ng v\'e0o ngh\u7881\'3f tron
